g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得成班毒能玩"},{"pid":"65799a3c62fac108afef75b699e2fab7447f2164","tid":98160,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得成班毒能玩</blockquote><br />\n等我第時打敗你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6cdc178b59309a89879ac39cb9afcb3fd43f93","tid":98160,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就選擇向神之一手飛行棋進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個我玩極都玩唔掂<br />\n成日去到最尾無限彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dc527acc89e64a73e2a9aa26da1e45c3d98e01","tid":98160,"uid":46832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:54:33.000Z","msg":"己經比alpha go 打殘啦，好sad"},{"pid":"a989a466a146c05ea28e961f4f22757d5e40207d","tid":98160,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>己經比alpha go 打殘啦，好sad</blockquote><br />\n有一集中國隊條友都講過電腦將會係最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcd29071a04842efa7e883588e9ee32d5f3db8b","tid":98160,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:13:42.000Z","msg":"香港的圍棋會所全部都係廢中廢老"},{"pid":"3f4fed4b8820fa934e15a800f38aed5200e15271","tid":98160,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ec13090ac331dedda752a31c975661cf3c34a97","tid":98160,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"波子棋神之一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f159da8e89d9ab1d76dee2c468f5bc5e42139917","tid":98160,"uid":71649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:23:55.000Z","msg":"第一次睇，動畫睇到21集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾鍾意佢表達嘅手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔會太注重喺盤棋度，反而喺音樂，氣氛，人物內心描寫帶你入戲<br />\n<br />\n描寫到圍棋好似個武林咁<br />\n<br />\n完全唔識圍棋嘅我都追得好緊湊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3eb250d74c8713694a91df5c0b45f9227194fd","tid":98160,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:25:25.000Z","msg":"巴打加油"},{"pid":"d6e3157598b781653c32b346600159d7863f2717","tid":98160,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捉棋有撚用咩<br />\n仲衰過識it</blockquote><br />\n緊係當興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4831c08e89f35bad59065245ea6d5eefad88eb87","tid":98160,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:33:57.000Z","msg":"鬥獸棋有冇神之前手？"},{"pid":"0a16370076cc97cc220e28250d54665ebf404d44","tid":98160,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬥獸棋有冇神之前手？</blockquote><br />\n都有掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過圍棋係咁多隻棋入面最複雜<br />\n唔係話食左對面隻王就完"},{"pid":"c8718ad423cde5f1a6b72334a1615361936cadae","tid":98160,"uid":78751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"加油，我嘅目標係麻雀嘅神之一手"},{"pid":"0e98db64c95585417ea3e1b6010a079660a14285","tid":98160,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"點解勁人一眼就睇到係唔係好棋？"},{"pid":"353abbf62b0acb27df3b9decdb0386bb00c2a454","tid":98160,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解勁人一眼就睇到係唔係好棋？</blockquote><br />\n應該因為果d係勁人"},{"pid":"932627398c207b9767d2d157eabec5ff62e6a724"